#: ../../incident-intelligence/create-configure-incident-policies.rst:114
msgid "Select :guilabel:`Add New Step` to add additional escalating steps with additional responders to your incident workflow."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Add New Step` を選択すると、インシデント・ワークフローに対応者を追加したエスカレーションステップを追加できます。"

#: ../../incident-intelligence/create-configure-incident-policies.rst:115
msgid "Select an elapsed time period in the list next to :guilabel:`If unacknowledged after`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`If unacknowledged after` の横のリストから経過時間を選択します。"

#: ../../incident-intelligence/create-configure-incident-policies.rst:116
msgid "Select :guilabel:`+ Add responders` to add responders."
msgstr "対応者を追加するには、:guilabel:`+ Add responders` を選択します。"

#: ../../incident-intelligence/create-configure-incident-policies.rst:117
msgid "Repeat these steps until you have a complete incident workflow for the incident policy."
msgstr "インシデント・ポリシーのインシデント・ワークフローが完成するまで、これらの手順を繰り返す。"

#: ../../incident-intelligence/create-configure-incident-policies.rst:122
msgid "Rank your incident policies to ensure alerts are appropriately routed"
